DEEPA THOMAS: Yeah.

00:22:57.295 --> 00:22:57.550
JAN YANEHIRO: OK.

00:22:57.550 --> 00:22:58.090
Good question.

00:22:58.090 --> 00:22:59.298
DEEPA THOMAS: Great question.

00:22:59.298 --> 00:23:00.820
JAN YANEHIRO: Deepa.

00:23:00.820 --> 00:23:03.730
DEEPA THOMAS: You know,
it's really my commitment

00:23:03.730 --> 00:23:06.970
to art and flavor
