00:23:23.980 --> 00:23:25.780
For me, it's essential.

00:23:25.780 --> 00:23:27.790
You know, my environment
is important.

00:23:27.790 --> 00:23:31.970
It affects my well-being, that
there's a candle on the table.

00:23:31.970 --> 00:23:35.170
There's maybe some fresh
