00:23:44.260 --> 00:23:46.720
I found that no matter
what difficulties

00:23:46.720 --> 00:23:50.160
I was facing, if I just made
my environment a little tidier

00:23:50.160 --> 00:23:52.680
or prettier or
maybe it's just me,

00:23:52.680 --> 00:23:55.960
but there's a part
that I actually

00:23:55.960 --> 00:24:00.280
write about the things we can
do to be a little more mindful.

