00:28:20.990 --> 00:28:23.310
You know, every day
is an opportunity.

00:28:23.310 --> 00:28:27.270
And just having become a
grandmother, I'm besot.

00:28:27.270 --> 00:28:30.960
but with this little
creature that something

00:28:30.960 --> 00:28:35.160
will happen in this journey
that is taking another turn yet.

00:28:35.160 --> 00:28:41.386
I never thought a grandchild
could change how I view life.

00:28:41.386 --> 00:28:42.510
It is completely different.

00:28:42.510 --> 00:28:48.010
Every window that was close in
my spirit has been blown open.

00:28:48.010 --> 00:28:51.040
So now the possibilities
are endless.

00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:53.430
I think the universe
is abundant.

00:28:53.430 --> 00:28:58.040
And I was saying earlier I
find if I leave my hands open,

00:28:58.040 --> 00:29:02.460
as in my mind, incredible
opportunity comes my way.

00:29:02.460 --> 00:29:06.480
So I'd love to do a line of
products that makes it easier

00:29:06.480 --> 00:29:09.330
