00:29:09.330 --> 00:29:12.600
And that to hopefully then
the sales of that will help

00:29:12.600 --> 00:29:15.810
us do even more good work, and
I think my cause will always

00:29:15.810 --> 00:29:16.870
be child related.

00:29:16.870 --> 00:29:20.700
It is unconscionable, as
I said, that our children

00:29:20.700 --> 00:29:24.480
are required to suffer in
a country that throws away

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:26.850
40% of its food.

00:29:26.850 --> 00:29:29.202
I think we all should
be obsessed with this.

