00:29:42.330 --> 00:29:45.120
having fast food
when you're young,

00:29:45.120 --> 00:29:48.180
how did your thinking
and reaction to food

00:29:48.180 --> 00:29:50.390
change once you started
preparing it for yourself

00:29:50.390 --> 00:29:51.535
and understanding recipes?

00:29:51.535 --> 00:29:52.410
DEEPA THOMAS: Oh wow.

00:29:52.410 --> 00:29:53.850
That's a great question.

00:29:53.850 --> 00:29:56.430
JAN YANEHIRO: But if you
read the book-- and I have--

00:29:56.430 --> 00:30:00.060
I'm going to admit
this for Deepa.

00:30:00.060 --> 00:30:03.840
