Now, what you're talking
about is a mindset,

00:37:44.910 --> 00:37:47.516
how we view comfort food.

00:37:47.516 --> 00:37:48.890
And what's the
need for comfort--

00:37:48.890 --> 00:37:51.600
what do we call comfort food?

00:37:51.600 --> 00:37:54.120
The foods you're describing--

00:37:54.120 --> 00:37:57.900
it's after a long day,
let's go have some drinks

00:37:57.900 --> 00:38:01.672
and eat rubbish is the way to
mitigate the stress that we

00:38:01.672 --> 00:38:03.630
probably should have
handled in a different way

00:38:03.630 --> 00:38:05.290
in the first place.

00:38:05.290 --> 00:38:07.380
I don't think it's
just India, but it's

00:38:07.380 --> 00:38:09.390
all countries that
are struggling

00:38:09.390 --> 00:38:13.770
with stress of
economic competition

00:38:13.770 --> 00:38:15.840
and the fear of loss--

00:38:15.840 --> 00:38:20.580
loss of a job, loss of
well-being, whatever it is.

00:38:20.580 --> 00:38:25.680
I don't think any one person can
change the ethos of a culture

00:38:25.680 --> 00:38:29.820
like India or America or
any country, but all of us

00:38:29.820 --> 00:38:33.060
together can ask the
question of ourselves.

00:38:33.060 --> 00:38:35.820
What are the tools we
have to handle threats?

00:38:35.820 --> 00:38:37.290
Simple question.

00:38:37.290 --> 00:38:38.160
I had the worst.

00:38:38.160 --> 00:38:39.960
In fact, I didn't
have any tools.

00:38:39.960 --> 00:38:41.970
Today I have a few more tools.

00:38:41.970 --> 00:38:44.730
And as I have more
tools to handle stress,

00:38:44.730 --> 00:38:45.870
I pay more attention.

00:38:45.870 --> 00:38:47.850
I'm more mindful.

00:38:47.850 --> 00:38:52.140
So until we as ordinary
citizens get mindful,

00:38:52.140 --> 00:38:54.450
I don't think brands
or anyone else

00:38:54.450 --> 00:38:57.660
is going to stop selling to--

00:38:57.660 --> 00:38:59.760
it's like drugs.

00:38:59.760 --> 00:39:01.380
Why do people buy drugs?

00:39:01.380 --> 00:39:03.580
They think it'll make
them feel better.

00:39:03.580 --> 00:39:06.510
Same thing-- junk
food and drugs are

00:39:06.510 --> 00:39:08.110
in the same area of the brain.

00:39:08.110 --> 00:39:12.480
Sugar is registered in exactly
the same place in the brain

00:39:12.480 --> 00:39:14.850
